record.field:
Write a professional email with the following details:
Topic: {topic}
Recipient: {recipient}
Key points: {key_points}
Tone: Professional and courteous

Please write a complete email with subject line and body.

Write a follow-up email about:
Subject: {subject}
Days since last contact: {days}
Additional context: {context}

Write a polite but effective follow-up email.

Generate a compelling product description for:
Product Name: {name}
Category: {category}
Key Features: {features}
Target Audience: {audience}

Create a description that highlights benefits and features.

Summarize the following text in a concise manner. Keep the key points and main message.

Text:
{text}

Analyze the sentiment of the following text.

Respond in JSON format:
{
  "sentiment": "positive/negative/neutral",
  "confidence": 0.0-1.0,
  "key_emotions": ["emotion1", "emotion2"],
  "explanation": "brief explanation"
}

Text:
{text}

Analyze this lead and provide a qualification assessment:

Lead Name: {name}
Company: {company}
Email: {email}
Notes: {notes}

Provide:
1. Lead Score (1-10)
2. Recommended Next Steps
3. Potential Objections
4. Suggested Approach

Break down this task into smaller, actionable subtasks:

Task: {task_name}
Description: {description}
Deadline: {deadline}

Create a list of subtasks with estimated time and priority.
